co.cask.cdap.api

Interface DatasetConfigurer

  • All Known Subinterfaces:
    ApplicationConfigurer, CustomActionConfigurer, FlowConfigurer, FlowletConfigurer, HttpServiceConfigurer, MapReduceConfigurer, MultiInputPipelineConfigurer, PipelineConfigurer, PluginConfigurer, ServiceConfigurer, SparkConfigurer, WorkerConfigurer, WorkflowConfigurer

    public interface DatasetConfigurer
    Provides the ability to add stream, datasets.

      • addDatasetModule

        @Beta
void addDatasetModule(String moduleName,
                         Class<? extends DatasetModule> moduleClass)

        Parameters:
        moduleName - Name of the module to deploy
        moduleClass - Class of the module

      • addDatasetType

        @Beta
void addDatasetType(Class<? extends Dataset> datasetClass)
        Adds a DatasetModule to be deployed automatically during application deployment, using Dataset as a base for the DatasetModule. The module will have a single dataset type identical to the name of the class in the datasetClass parameter.
        Parameters:
        datasetClass - Class of the dataset; module name will be the same as the class in the parameter

      • createDataset

        @Beta
void createDataset(String datasetName,
                      String typeName,
                      DatasetProperties properties)
        Adds a Dataset instance, created automatically if absent in the CDAP namespace. If the Dataset instance already exists, this updates the existing instance with the new properties. See DatasetDefinition for details.
        Parameters:
        datasetName - name of the dataset instance
        typeName - name of the dataset type
        properties - dataset instance properties

      • createDataset

        void createDataset(String datasetName,
                 String typeName)
        Adds a Dataset instance with DatasetProperties.EMPTY created automatically if absent in the CDAP namespace. If the Dataset instance already exists, this updates the existing instance with the new properties.
        Parameters:
        datasetName - name of the dataset instance
        typeName - name of the dataset type

      • createDataset

        void createDataset(String datasetName,
                 Class<? extends Dataset> datasetClass,
                 DatasetProperties props)
        Deploys a Dataset type using the datasetClass parameter (see addDatasetType(Class)), then adds a Dataset instance, if absent in the CDAP namespace, or if the Dataset instance already exists, updates the existing instance with the new properties.
        Parameters:
        datasetName - dataset instance name
        datasetClass - dataset class to create the Dataset type from
        props - dataset instance properties

      • createDataset

        Parameters:
        datasetName - dataset instance name
        datasetClass - dataset class to create the Dataset type from
